{"tid":2008174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五四運動之「火燒趙家樓 痛打章宗祥」","createTime":"2020-05-09T00:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T16:57:01.000Z","uid":212731,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"18bf8518cee71e2c866e46b2f54a93fa74f49b50","tid":2008174,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:07:09.000Z","msg":"5月4日，上午10時，各校學生召開碰頭會，商定遊行路線。下午1點，北京大學等十三所院校三千餘名學生匯集天安門，舉行了聲勢浩大的示威活動。提出了「外爭國權，內除國賊」、「取消二十一條」、「拒絕合約簽字」等口號。學生代表要求會見四國公使，但由於禮拜天三國大使不在館內，巡捕房不准學生前往，最後僅能到美國使館前。學生們在美國使館前高喊在「大美國萬歲！威大總統萬歲！大中華民國萬歲！世界永久和平萬歲」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後，隊伍中喊出一句：「去找曹汝霖算賬去！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />矛盾遂轉向「內懲國賊」&mdash;&mdash;學生開始向位於北京長安街東端之北的趙家樓曹宅所在地移動，一路上高喊「收回山東權利」、「拒絕在巴黎和會上簽字」、「廢除二十一條」、「抵制日貨」、「寧肯玉碎，勿為瓦全」、「外爭國權，內懲國賊」、「還我青島」等口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，並且要求懲辦交通總長曹汝霖、幣制局總裁陸宗輿、駐日公使章宗祥。下午兩點多鐘，大規模遊行隊伍到達曹宅，數百名軍警早把胡同口封住了，隊伍不得入內。學生向軍警講明來意說：「我們是愛國學生，來這裏是找曹總長談談國事，交換意見，要他愛中國。我們學生手無寸鐵，你們也是中國人，難道你們不愛中國嗎？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />軍警於是放行。<span style=\"color: red;\">學生進入胡同，發生暴亂痛打了在曹家串門的章宗祥，並火燒曹宅，引發「火燒趙家樓」事件。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當遊行隊伍逼近曹宅，只見大門緊閉。如何打入？「突然有領隊某君，奮不顧身，縱步躍上（大門）右邊小窗戶。」「不顧一切地跳下去，迅速而機警地把大門開了，於是大隊學生蜂擁而入」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n此時，曹汝霖與章宗祥正在客廳談話，忽聽嘈雜之聲。曹汝霖的父親見狀不好，趕緊指揮兩人藏起來。曹汝霖父親曹成達與闖進來的學生周旋。學生找不到賣國賊，氣得摔瓷器，砸玻璃，翻箱倒櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，搗毀汽車。學生在曹父房間，將櫥子裏的燕窩銀耳等補品踐踏粉碎。有人在客廳放火，聽說着火了，藏在鍋爐房的章宗祥溜了出來，被眼尖的學生髮現，誤以為是曹汝霖，逮住他，一頓暴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有人打了他一棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，輕微腦震盪。<br />\n<br />\n火燒趙家樓那一幕，王曉明《五四運動中的高師學生》文中這樣描述：匡互生取出準備好的火柴，和周予同一起撕下床上的帳子。這時擔任此次示威指揮的北大學生段錫朋看到，立即過來阻止說：「我負不了這個責任！」匡互生說：「誰要你負責任，你也確定負不了責任。」說着，即將火柴點燃，熊熊怒火和着學生們的憤怒沖天而起。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n火，出現了。火燒趙家樓，這是革命之火，民主之光，當然，更是愛國學生的激情燃燒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學生遊行活動受到廣泛關注，各界人士給予關注和支持，抗議逮捕學生，蔡元培、朱家驊等「歐美同學會」會員（時會長蔡元培）當時為了營救學生，不惜發動全國工商界罷工罷市，上至政府官員；下至務農人員。"},{"pid":"1afbcb7224b8ad6f136e2dc07fe910c03fd9efea","tid":2008174,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec55246fe3377cd0e75c6fd2068abaf0f2dee2fd","tid":2008174,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:11:14.000Z","msg":"唔敢打洋人<br />\n<br />\n轉頭打國人<br />\n<br />\n黑警作風 哈哈"},{"pid":"505e21b648bfddd0c43a38e7a84cc7bad867ea16","tid":2008174,"uid":65770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:15:12.000Z","msg":"炒車打錯人"},{"pid":"606da05c2d2cb6155789768ff103e612ac8d9161","tid":2008174,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"505e21b648bfddd0c43a38e7a84cc7bad867ea16","tid":2008174,"uid":65770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:15:12.000Z","msg":"炒車打錯人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:20:36.000Z","msg":"打錯鄭若驊同林鄭既分別"},{"pid":"c5c61bdaf8ef4618a98f776df173b0fbc6346309","tid":2008174,"uid":271894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:25:15.000Z","msg":"史上有冇姓何既賣國賊？"},{"pid":"545aea684da20c50787f2867b676ea8331cb445c","tid":2008174,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd19c7ae18d746971015f7d99efca44eedb66de","tid":2008174,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec55246fe3377cd0e75c6fd2068abaf0f2dee2fd","tid":2008174,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:11:14.000Z","msg":"唔敢打洋人<br />\n<br />\n轉頭打國人<br />\n<br />\n黑警作風 哈哈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T13:22:17.000Z","msg":"咁義和團同呢單啱你口味<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%AB%E7%83%A7%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E4%BB%A3%E5%8A%9E%E5%A4%84%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%2583%25A7%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259B%25BD%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%258A%259E%25E5%25A4%2584%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=3c63628e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%AB%E7%83%A7%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E4%BB%A3%E5%8A%9E%E5%A4%84%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a><br />\n不過紅衛兵打嗰條英國佬抵打，咁撚親支 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299cb4d2318981878b1db91d714d98b7b1ac4a07","tid":2008174,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfd19c7ae18d746971015f7d99efca44eedb66de","tid":2008174,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec55246fe3377cd0e75c6fd2068abaf0f2dee2fd","tid":2008174,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:11:14.000Z","msg":"唔敢打洋人<br />\n<br />\n轉頭打國人<br />\n<br />\n黑警作風 哈哈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T13:22:17.000Z","msg":"咁義和團同呢單啱你口味<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%AB%E7%83%A7%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E4%BB%A3%E5%8A%9E%E5%A4%84%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%2583%25A7%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259B%25BD%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%258A%259E%25E5%25A4%2584%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=3c63628e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%AB%E7%83%A7%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E4%BB%A3%E5%8A%9E%E5%A4%84%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a><br />\n不過紅衛兵打嗰條英國佬抵打，咁撚親支 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T13:34:02.000Z","msg":"打唔撚死佢真係可惜"},{"pid":"bbe6642369f15fe42c788446d5d324400938131b","tid":2008174,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T13:37:39.000Z","msg":"《匪徒頌》寫於1919年末。 詩歌為抗議日本新聞界對五四運動後的中國學生的誣衊而作。 詩人以熱情的呼喊、憤激的反語,讚頌了古往今來一切&ldquo;政治革命&rdquo;、 &ldquo;社會革命&rdquo;、 &ldquo;宗教革命&rdquo;、 &ldquo;學說革命&rdquo;、 &ldquo;文藝革命&rdquo;、 &ldquo;教育革命&rdquo;的&ldquo;匪徒們&rdquo;,對 他們三呼萬歲!充分體現了向舊傳統、舊制度勇猛挑戰的叛逆精神。 其中對&ldquo;實行共產主義的列寧&rdquo;的歌頌,更顯示了詩人在十月革命的影響下對社會主義的朦朧嚮往。<br />\n<br />\n反抗王政的罪魁北克，敢行稱亂的克倫威爾呀！<br />\n私行割據的草寇，抗糧拒稅的華盛頓呀！<br />\n圖謀恢復的頑民，死有餘辜的黎塞爾呀！<br />\n西北南東去來今，一切政治革命的匪徒們呀！<br />\n萬歲！ 萬歲！ 萬歲！"},{"pid":"7f227a8df40184c041f1691f910043ddc42c8ea7","tid":2008174,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T13:42:45.000Z","msg":"外爭港權，內除港賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f520fa9cf45beb9b2d91f02d1fc0381dffec2a81","tid":2008174,"uid":48040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T13:43:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4nzUThz8BvI&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=3c68a1a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C7YbpoujZlw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC7YbpoujZlw&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=dd5b475e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C7YbpoujZlw</a>"},{"pid":"b36ab0edc92925267f821508fd64f72dbf931120","tid":2008174,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007612f5b913964788f9acb04c32dcc255d5b1b3","tid":2008174,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T16:57:01.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n推<br />\n推<br />\n推"}]}